 This will affect the Ogies and Bethal interchanges as an overpass bridge will be erected. The N12 leading in both directions will be closed on Saturday 18 May from 00:00 – 00:00 and Sunday 19 May from 00:00 – 15:00. Commuters will be diverted to use the N12 eastbound Ogies and Bethal offramp from Johannesburg to eMalahleni and the N12 westbound, eMalahleni West and Ogies offramp coming from eMalahleni towards Johannesburg. Motorists are urged to drive with caution and adhere to traffic regulations.     Parents frustrated by a lack of space in Middelburg schools Traffic officers to appear in court for corruption #TrafficAlert: Two dead in Kranspoort accidents VIDEO: Two perish after truck jack-knifes • Save our standby number (072 248 3855) and send us a WhatsApp message with the words “Add me” to be added to our broadcast list. • Like us on Facebook, follow us on Twitter and Instagram. • Subscribe to our YouTube channel. • Click on the link to subscribe to our bi-weekly newsletter via email. Contact our news room on our 24 hr standby number 072 248 3855, or send a mail to our editor tobie@mobserver.co.za